## 6. Implementation Plan

### 6.1. Phase 1: Core (MVP)

- Creating a local SQLite database for "Text ↔ Key" mapping for Python
- Developing a code parser based on AST (Abstract Syntax Tree)
- Basic compressor and decompressor

### 6.2. Phase 2: Logger

- VS Code plugin that visually substitutes keys with text
- Change logging system through keys

### 6.3. Phase 3: Protocol

- Implementation of push/pull protocol based on key list comparison
- Integration with existing platforms (GitHub API)

### 6.4. Phase 4: AI Integration

- Key documentation for AI models
- Fine-tuning model for native key understanding

